                        <interp inst="t18480403-1163-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>.</hi> Aged 22.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18480403-1163-punishment-172" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18480403-1163-punishment-172" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480403-1163-punishment-172" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1163-18480403 t18480403-1163-punishment-172"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
